text.tspan: Our Nirvanic Insight Quest aims to understand and
comprehend the complex human behavior into
easily understandable traits. It focusses on assess
ing the unique traits centric to one’s core, social and
work life.
An assessment to understand the natural inclina
tion of an individual. It focusses on exploring the
core interest area of an individual. It enables the
individual to understand their dominant orienta
tion.
To understand the cognitive ability of a person, our
Core-Cognition Test aims to explore the natural
tendency of a person. It assesses the individual’s
abilities in three varied domains through unconven
tional testing methodology.
Progressive Matrices test tries to assess the indi
vidual’s abstract intelligence. It tries to assess the
individual’s ability to analyze information, detect
patterns and identify relationships to solve com
plex problems.
